## 5. Win Conditions & Campaign State
How the game detects a victor and advances the external campaign.

**Supporting Code:**
- **In-Game Elimination:** `src/engine/EffectEngine.js` (`_checkWinCondition`)
  - Triggered whenever LP reaches 0 (`dealDamageToLP`) or a player attempts to draw but has no cards (`drawCards`).
  - Sets `gameState.gameOver = true` and fires the `GAME_OVER` event.
- **Campaign Progression:** `src/ui/CampaignUI.js` / `src/ui/WarCampaignUI.js`
  - Listens for `GAME_OVER`.
  - Determines the winner, logs the result to `CampaignData` or `WarCampaignData`, awards Victory Points (VP) and Landmark placement rights.
  - Triggers the next round of Deckbuilding or determines the ultimate campaign victor.
